metadata.name: Sea trials of the «Titanic»
metadata.description:
April 2, 1912. «Titanic» departs Belfast on her sea trials.

After the completion of sea trials, «Titanic» was issued an official paper authorising her operation for one year, and from that moment she officially entered service as «White Star Line’s»flagship liner. 

Watercolor painting 35,5x51 cm. The purchaser of this NFT will also receive a physical drawing.
